data.description: Home, sweet home! This charming residence with a 2-car garage and a mature front yard is the one! Discover a spacious open floor plan filled with natural and recessed lighting, accented walls, tall ceilings, a bay window, and tile flooring. The gourmet kitchen is a homemaker's delight, featuring SS appliances, farmhouse sink, quartz counters, beautiful wood cabinetry with crown molding, a subway tile backsplash, and an island with a breakfast bar for casual dining. Make the den into a home office or another bedroom! Retreat to the primary bedroom that highlights a sitting area with a bay window, backyard access, and a private bathroom with dual sinks and a walk-in closet. The perfectly sized backyard invites you to unwind under the covered patio while drinking your favorite beverage!
